_ar":"ارجا","root":"rjA^","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He postponed, put off, deferred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delayed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, Mgh, Msb, K,) an affair, (ISk, S, Mgh, K,) and a person; (TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArjY","text_ar":"ارجى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (ISk, S, Mgh, Msb, K:) but the former is the better: the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irojaA='N","text_ar":"اـِرْجَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) It is said in the Kur [xxxiii. 51], accord. to different readings,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turojiY'u mano ta$aA='u minohun~a","text_ar":"تُرْجِىءُ مَنْ تَشَا=ءُ مِنْهُنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turojiY","text_ar":"تُرْجِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou mayest put off whom thou wilt of them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"addressed peculiarly to the Prophet, exclusively of others of his people. (Zj, TA.) [See also an ex. in the Kur vii. 108 and xxvi. 35; and the various readings mentioned by Bd in the former instance.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arojaA^ato","text_ar":"اَرْجَاَتْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel, S, K, and in like manner a pregnant female [of any kind], TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, near to bringing forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arojato","text_ar":"اَرْجَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) AA says the former. (S.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArjA^","text_ar":"ارجا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a hunter or sportsman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was unsuccessful, getting no game;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArjY","text_ar":"ارجى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) or you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArjA^ AlS~ayoda","text_ar":"ارجا الصَّيْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjw","text_ar":"رجو"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArjY","text_ar":"ارجى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~ayoda","text_ar":"الصَّيْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K in that art.)"}],"source_refs":["ISk","S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}